title: Baby, Don't You Like This Beat?
content: Chappell Roan @ Hollywood Palladium 11/18/2022 by Justin Higuchi, via Flickr (https://www.flickr.com/photos/jus10h/) Over in Ask MetaFilter, member The Adventure Begins is looking for music recommendations similar to Chappell Roan's "Hot To Go" aka "high energy synth pop bops by girls". Come share your suggestions and see what others have recommended!
author: Brandon Blatcher
